-- Molycorp Inc CEO Tells WSJ China Not Using Rare Earths as `a Weapon'
-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 2010-10-20T22:37:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-20/molycorp-chief-executive-tells-wsj-china-not-using-rare-earths-as-weapon.html
China is not using its position in
the rare-earths market as “a weapon,” the Wall Street Journal
cited Molycorp Inc. Chief Executive Officer Mark Smith as saying
in an interview.   Smith praised China for enforcing industry rules against
smuggling and pollution, saying that he “admires” the steps
the nation is taking, according to the WSJ.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  